Foreign buyers will be charged a higher fee when buying property in the UK
Under the new Conservative plans, foreign buyers will be charged a higher fee for buying property in the UK, and the extra money will be used to help the homeless
This move will neutralize the success of Corbyn's attempt to attract young voters
The increase in the fee will be imposed on those who do not pay tax in the United Kingdom.
